 <BMarkdown>## Parameters
 
 | Parameter         | Type                          | Description                                                                                     | Default      |
 |-------------------|-------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------|
 | `Variant`         | `ProgressIndicatorVariant`    | The style of the progress indicator: `Circular` or `Linear`.                                    | `Circular`   |
 | `Indeterminate`   | `bool`                        | Whether the progress indicator is indeterminate (animated with no fixed progress).              | `false`      |
 | `Progress`        | `double`                      | The progress value (0.0 to 1.0) for determinate indicators.                                      | `0.0`        |
 | `Style`           | `string?`                    | Custom CSS styles to apply to the root container of the progress indicator.                     | `null`       |
 | `Class`           | `string?`                    | Custom CSS class to apply to the root container of the progress indicator.                      | `null`       |
 </BMarkdown>
